{"word":"οὐκοῦν","slug":"οὐκοῦν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὐϰοῦν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὖν\">οὖν</a></el>] a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> particle anticipating an affirmative answer to a query, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκοῦν\">οὐκοῦν</a> βασιλεὺς εἶ συ</el>; so you are a king, then? <b><a href='B:500 18:37'>J 18:37</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐκέτι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Οὐλαμμαούς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}